EESchema-LIBRARY Version 2.4
#encoding utf-8
#
# Quartz Tuner - KiCad Symbol Library
# STM32G491RET6 + Si5351A + AD5933 crystal parameter analyzer
#
# This is a placeholder symbol library. Full KiCad schematic files
# should be created using KiCad EDA. The pin assignments and
# connections are documented in the README.md pin tables.
#

# STM32G491RET6 (LQFP-64)
DEF STM32G491RET6 U 0 40 Y Y 1 F N
F0 "U" 0 0 60 H V C CNN
F1 "STM32G491RET6" 0 -100 60 H V C CNN
DRAW
S -400 800 400 -800 0 1 0 f
X PA0 1 -500 700 100 R 50 50 1 1 I
X PA1 2 -500 650 100 R 50 50 1 1 I
X PA2 3 -500 600 100 R 50 50 1 1 I
X PA3 4 -500 550 100 R 50 50 1 1 I
X PA4 5 -500 500 100 R 50 50 1 1 I
X PA5 6 -500 450 100 R 50 50 1 1 I
X PA6 7 -500 400 100 R 50 50 1 1 I
X PA7 8 -500 350 100 R 50 50 1 1 I
X VDD 9 -500 -700 100 R 50 50 1 1 W
X VSS 10 -500 -750 100 R 50 50 1 1 W
ENDDRAW
ENDDEF

# Si5351A (MSOP-10)
DEF Si5351A U 0 40 Y Y 1 F N
F0 "U" 0 0 60 H V C CNN
F1 "Si5351A" 0 -100 60 H V C CNN
DRAW
S -200 300 200 -300 0 1 0 f
X SDA 1 -300 200 100 R 50 50 1 1 B
X SCL 2 -300 150 100 R 50 50 1 1 I
X CLK0 3 300 200 100 L 50 50 1 1 O
X CLK1 4 300 150 100 L 50 50 1 1 O
X CLK2 5 300 100 100 L 50 50 1 1 O
X OEA 6 -300 -100 100 R 50 50 1 1 I
X RST 7 -300 -200 100 R 50 50 1 1 I
X XA 8 300 -100 100 L 50 50 1 1 I
X XB 9 300 -200 100 L 50 50 1 1 I
X VIN 10 -300 -50 100 R 50 50 1 1 W
ENDDRAW
ENDDEF

# AD5933 (TSSOP-16)
DEF AD5933 U 0 40 Y Y 1 F N
F0 "U" 0 0 60 H V C CNN
F1 "AD5933" 0 -100 60 H V C CNN
DRAW
S -300 400 300 -400 0 1 0 f
X SDA 1 -400 300 100 R 50 50 1 1 B
X SCL 2 -400 250 100 R 50 50 1 1 I
X MCLK 3 -400 150 100 R 50 50 1 1 I
X VIN+ 4 -400 50 100 R 50 50 1 1 I
X VIN- 5 -400 -50 100 R 50 50 1 1 I
X RFB 6 -400 -150 100 R 50 50 1 1 I
X RSET 7 -400 -250 100 R 50 50 1 1 I
X CTRL 8 400 300 100 L 50 50 1 1 I
X RST 9 400 200 100 L 50 50 1 1 I
X VDD 10 400 100 100 L 50 50 1 1 W
X GND 11 400 -100 100 L 50 50 1 1 W
ENDDRAW
ENDDEF